divs: Sighting DetailsBetween 8pm-9pm, facing East first. My fiance and I were video taping and photograping the sky. I took multiple photos in which after observed showed many Bright objects in the East direction and the West direction. We are often outside taking videos and observing the nights sky. We were not very surprised to see these photos, as we have had multiple sights.
Summary: Multiple photos of bright ufo lights facing East and West behind my home on 10/16/2011
